{"tid":2322101,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"league of legends(手機版) - Wild Rift 終於出左啦","createTime":"2020-12-12T05:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T23:41:01.000Z","uid":260581,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1f446ab953b4816e907c569751b99d54f199fc67","tid":2322101,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hf35a9y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhf35a9y.png&h=0c93b88c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0U78We.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0U78We.png&h=44e89db4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k85y4uB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk85y4uB.png&h=0fcd7a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVxhMHX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVxhMHX.png&h=d0027f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原先上年話今年4月出<br />\n然後早幾日終於出左<br />\n而家係patch 1.1 ，城仔同你率先試玩<br />\n呢個就係個登入介面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eG7Ywaq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeG7Ywaq.png&h=bc966c53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHYT4vr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHYT4vr.png&h=09649b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dveHdoN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdveHdoN.png&h=1cf8c6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時可以玩既英<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kpTj38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kpTj38.png&h=e0dd5616&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HDQnhv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HDQnhv.png&h=b52834ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hooT4vR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhooT4vR.png&h=d92713cb&s={SIZE}\" />我最近有玩過pc版 知道改過<br />\n我覺得而家d裝係跟返好耐之前d patch<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LazLWmz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLazLWmz.png&h=49514de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJ4 cataclysm <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/doWB21A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdoWB21A.png&h=e26de4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFizz Chum the waters<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7Qy5au.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7Qy5au.png&h=88dcc3b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyACNoR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyACNoR.png&h=462c66f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUNxBnn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUNxBnn.png&h=d3c16c99&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pzgiAK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pzgiAK.png&h=9adce6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ts79DAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fts79DAM.png&h=03685d62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rMFbRVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMFbRVN.png&h=8edbb944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老實講 我由s2頭玩呢隻game<br />\n玩到兩年前就停左<br />\n有時覺得riot改到d英好on9<br />\n有時nerf到覺得變左質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手機版確實有d重拾我對呢隻game既熱愛<br />\n你問我玩左幾場係幾好玩<br />\n有玩過lol既好玩就上手<br />\n本來以為d mechanics 高既英 換落手機好難玩<br />\n但又ok wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如lee sin 既qwr ward kick<br />\nAkali, j4, 都幾好玩<br />\n技能flash 都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要㩒既金身，放ignite，flash<br />\n操作亦唔太難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻game個缺點就係一場有d耐<br />\n有時玩成30分鐘一場 望住個細mon<br />\n玩到對眼好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過用手機玩真係方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df628367b223ca2c8bff217a846f8a5320f268a7","tid":2322101,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"城仔，讀書啦<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/08/133427_40ef945b4b560bfc9a04b6135b35787f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F08%2F133427_40ef945b4b560bfc9a04b6135b35787f.gif&h=c92a2d10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8fc43a19c42804771523ccf2a42ef817586379f","tid":2322101,"uid":260581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"df628367b223ca2c8bff217a846f8a5320f268a7","tid":2322101,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"城仔，讀書啦<img src=\"https://img.eservice